# Answer Composer — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

**Layer 11 — Evidence-Bound Answer Composer** per §2.11. This module is responsible for orchestrating the final Answer generation. It takes the output from the [AdjudicationEngine](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/engine.py#30-278) and uses the `gemini-2.0-flash` model to format the claims into a coherent answer with strict sentence-level citations.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    SQO["Structured Query Object"] --> COMPOSER["AnswerComposer.generate()"]
    ADJ["Adjudication Result"] --> COMPOSER
    
    COMPOSER --> COV_CHK{"Coverage < 0.60?"}
    
    COV_CHK -->|"Yes"| FALLBACK["Return Insufficient Evidence String"]
    COV_CHK -->|"No"| PROMPT["Assign IDs [C1], [C2]<br/>Format Constraints"]
    
    PROMPT --> LLM["Gemini 2.0 Flash<br/>JSON Mode"]
    LLM --> PARSE["Parse FinalAnswer"]
    
    FALLBACK --> OUT["FinalAnswer DTO"]
    PARSE --> OUT
```

