## Bug Fixes During Implementation

1. **`ingestion.config` import**: Mistakenly imported `INGESTION_CONFIG` instead of `settings`. Fixed to accurately access the `gemini_api_key`.
2. **[QueryConstraints](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/schemas.py#42-49) vs [TemporalConstraint](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/schemas.py#35-40)**: Updating the test mocks to correctly instantiate Pydantic nested models [TemporalConstraint(after="2024")](file:///c:/HelioX/query_pipeline/schemas.py#35-40) rather than passing raw strings, which caused validation failures.
3. **[SupportingSpan](file:///c:/HelioX/workers/schemas.py#33-39) properties**: The underlying core schemas expect `.start` and `.end`, but the generator temporarily used `.start_idx`. Unified to use `.start` and `.end`.

